original_title: Trans Entities: The Nasty Love of Papí and Wil
overview: This movie by Morty Diamond captures a real couple discussing their sex, sexuality and gender identity. Papi’ and Wil show us everything from the negotiation of a role play scene, to the scene itself and the after care when the scene is over.
title: Trans Entities: The Nasty Love of Papí and Wil
